# 🚗 Thuva Waves - Ride Booking Platform

A full-stack MERN ride-booking application inspired by Uber/PickMe, connecting passengers with nearby drivers in real time.

![MERN Stack](https://img.shields.io/badge/Stack-MERN-green)
