## 📁 Project Structure

```
thuva-waves/
├── frontend/
│   ├── src/
│   │   ├── components/       # Reusable UI components
│   │   ├── pages/            # Home, Login, Dashboards, etc.
│   │   ├── hooks/            # Custom React hooks
│   │   ├── services/         # Axios API calls
│   │   ├── context/          # Auth & global state
│   │   └── utils/
│   ├── .env
│   └── package.json
│
├── backend/
│   ├── controllers/
│   ├── models/                # Mongoose schemas
│   ├── routes/
│   ├── middleware/            # Auth, error handling, validation
│   ├── services/
│   ├── sockets/               # Socket.io handlers
│   ├── config/                # DB, Cloudinary, Firebase config
│   ├── .env
│   └── server.js
│
└── README.md
```

### Frontend Pages
- Home
- Login / Register
- Passenger Dashboard
- Driver Dashboard
- Admin Dashboard
- Ride Booking
- Ride Tracking
- Profile
- Ride History
- Earnings
- Analytics

